TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi beforefieldinit PropertyConstants extends System.Object

Docs.summary: Represents the constants for all out-of-box profile property names.

remarks.para: All fields are string values that represent the names of properties that hold profile information. These constants can be passed into the indexer of a profile object, such as the object.
